	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_WORKERS_FACULTIES_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Share and Share Alike</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_WORKERS_FACULTIES_HELP">
			<Text>The construction of our Worker's Faculties in all major Cities is nearing final phase completion, comrade! Na Zdorovie! Or... whatever it is we say.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_WORKERS_FACULTIES_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Invest {1_YieldCost} in order to generate +10% [ICON_FOOD] Food in Cities with Factories.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_WORKERS_FACULTIES_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Invest {1_YieldCost} in order to allow Towns to yield +4 [ICON_RESEARCH] Science.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_WORKERS_FACULTIES_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Your [ICON_DIPLOMAT] Civil Servants generate -1 [ICON_GOLD] Gold but +4 [ICON_FOOD] Food. </Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_WORKERS_FACULTIES_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Now we have built the housing for our workers, we need to fill it! See to it that everything is done to encourage our citizens to become parents, comrade!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_WORKERS_FACULTIES_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Cheers indeed, comrade Domestic Advisor. Now we must build these tenements in the Towns as well!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_IDEOLOGY_WORKERS_FACULTIES_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Housing is a major concern going forwards. We need to ensure that we never lack for provision; that we are never behind the curve. See that our best minds are on solving that problem, comrade!</Text>
		</Row>
